Order much less than you think you need.
The ethiopian beer was light, floral, and would be great on on a hot day.
Service: We went there for my daughter's 4th birthday and the staff went all out.
I don't think ethiopia has many deserts so the gave us a giant loaf of bread.
It was great.
Location: They are located in a typical low rent strip mall and not impressive at all.
If you are influenced by fancy plates and napkins, head to the strip.
If you only concerned by the quality of the food, go here.

